Cante "Russia with Love".

415
00:24:04.164 --> 00:24:05.291
Obrigado, rapazes.

416
00:24:06.166 --> 00:24:07.918
<i>Os Beatles eram audaciosos.</i>

417
00:24:08.168 --> 00:24:10.504
<i>Quando eram entrevistados,
